Package: hub
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ruby, git-core
Description: a command line utility which adds GitHub knowledge to git
 Hub enhances various Git commands with GitHub remote expansion.
 .
 It provides commands to make forking, fetching, browsing
 and creating projects on GitHub easier.
